videos.description: UCLA's Charisma Osborne knocks down a 3-pointer from the wing in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Charisma Osborne stretches UCLA's lead with 3-pointer) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charisma Osborne stretches UCLA's lead with 3-pointer

videos.description: UConn's Caroline Ducharme pulls up from the corner and hits the 3-pointer late in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Caroline Ducharme rattles in 3-pointer just before the half) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Caroline Ducharme rattles in 3-pointer just before the half

videos.description: Evina Westbrook and Aaliyah Edwards score on back-to-back possessions to help UConn take a lead vs. UCLA.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Westbrook, Edwards get back-to-back buckets to put UConn up) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook, Edwards get back-to-back buckets to put UConn up

videos.description: UConn's Evina Westbrook appears to get fouled as she tries for a layup, but the officials don't call it, and Geno Auriemma gets a technical foul for voicing his frustrations.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Geno Auriemma gets a technical after voicing his unhappiness on a no-call) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Geno Auriemma gets a technical after voicing his unhappiness on a no-call

videos.description: UConn's Olivia Nelson-Ododa bounces a pass to a driving Christyn Williams for a bucket and the foul to extend the Huskies' lead late in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Williams comes up with clutch and-1 for UConn) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams comes up with clutch and-1 for UConn
